item.title: 612: Framework's Matt Hartley
item.description: Mike sits down with Matt Hartley of Framework to discuss some of their exciting new announcements, some Linux goodness & of course an obligatory Rust shoutout. Feed: https://feeds.jupiterbroadcasting.com/coder

item.title: Lip-Bu Tan's Intel
item.description:
Intel has a new CEO! And it's Lip-Bu Tan. We had assumed it would not be Lip-Bu--he was such a clear front-runner that the more time passed the less likely it seemed it would be him... and yet! Bryan and Adam were joined by Reuter's Max Cherney to discuss.

In addition to Bryan Cantrill and Adam Leventhal, our esteemed guest was Max Cherney; we were also joined by Bryan Russett, and Alex Kesling... Feed: https://feeds.transistor.fm/oxide-and-friends
